{"title":"上传博客的教程","uid":"b758b30cf4b0783e0b607f6f8db1e577","slug":"上传博客的教程","date":"2025-08-10T20:26:31.000Z","updated":"2025-08-11T07:05:40.711Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/上传博客的教程.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h2 id=\"以后写文章的流程\"><a href=\"#以后写文章的流程\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"以后写文章的流程\"></a><strong>以后写文章的流程</strong></h2><ol>\n<li><code>npx hexo new post &quot;文章标题&quot;</code></li>\n<li>编辑 <code>source/_posts/文章标题.md</code></li>\n<li><code>git add . &amp;&amp; git commit -m &quot;update post&quot; &amp;&amp; git push</code></li>\n<li>等 1~2 分钟，GitHub Pages 自动更新</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"在其他设备上推送博客的流程\"><a href=\"#在其他设备上推送博客的流程\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"在其他设备上推送博客的流程\"></a>在其他设备上推送博客的流程</h2><ol>\n<li><p>安装git、node.js、npm</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>使用git -v, node -v, npm -v检查是否安装成功</p></blockquote>\n</li>\n<li><p>选择一个目录打开 git bash，执行</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git clone https:<span class=\"comment\">//github.com/Leeway2ZC/hexo-blog.git</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>进入仓库目录 <code>cd hexo-blog</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>安装项目依赖 <code>npm install</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>在Git中设置本地用户名和邮箱</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>配置全局Git用户名</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git config --global user.name <span class=\"string\">&quot;Leeway2ZC&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>配置全局Git邮箱</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git config --global user.email <span class=\"string\">&quot;leeway2zc@gmail.com&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>然后就可以按照上面的流程写文章啦</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"关于配置图床\"><a href=\"#关于配置图床\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"关于配置图床\"></a>关于配置图床</h2><ol>\n<li>安装PicGo</li>\n<li>配置PicGo<ol>\n<li>使用ini文件设置腾讯云Cos</li>\n<li>设置Server修改监听端口与Typora保持一致</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>配置Typora<ol>\n<li>修改偏好设置中的图像</li>\n<li>修改为上传图片，上传服务更改为PicGo</li>\n<li>验证图片上传选项</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<img src=\"https://leeway2zcblog-1373523181.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/img/image-20250811005047923.png\" alt=\"image-20250811005047923\" style=\"zoom:50%;\" />\n\n<h2 id=\"注意事项\"><a href=\"#注意事项\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"注意事项\"></a>注意事项</h2><ul>\n<li><p>如果在另一台设备上做了修改，那么写文章前先要拉取最新代码</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git pull origin main</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>从而确保代码库是最新的，避免冲突</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n","feature":true,"text":"以后写文章的流程 npx hexo new post \"文章标题\" 编辑 source/_posts/文章标题.md git add . && git comm...","permalink":"/post/上传博客的教程","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":746,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BB%A5%E5%90%8E%E5%86%99%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E7%9A%84%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">以后写文章的流程</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%9C%A8%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E4%B8%8A%E6%8E%A8%E9%80%81%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">在其他设备上推送博客的流程</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">关于配置图床</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E4%BA%8B%E9%A1%B9\"><span class=\"toc-text\">注意事项</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Aurora","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{"title":"笔记本测试","uid":"eb6c270e6e202b09549a3e6c4f7822e9","slug":"笔记本测试","date":"2025-08-11T14:34:23.000Z","updated":"2025-08-11T07